                        </h1>


                        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-500">
                            We got sick of LinkedIn thought leadership, so we
                            made a satirical social network where anyone can be
                            a Thought Leader, Disruptor, or Titan of Industry.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8">
